{"tid":2299584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【愛侵力要輸幾多次】賓夕法尼亞州確認拜登擊敗特朗普　州長已簽確認書","createTime":"2020-11-25T02:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T02:21:28.000Z","uid":231908,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e027d079e7b3581a540a876dc3d2f209eb2f807e","tid":2299584,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:00:01.000Z","msg":"美國賓夕法尼亞州確認該關鍵州份的大選結果，民主黨的拜登擊敗爭取連任的總統特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n州長在社交專頁說已根據聯邦法例要求，為拜登及副手賀錦麗的名單簽署確認書。另一關鍵戰場密歇根州，選舉委員會早前亦確認拜登勝出。美聯社推算，拜登共取得306張選舉人票，遠多於270張的當選門檻，特朗普就有232張。<br />\n<br />\n監督大選後權力過渡的美國聯邦總務署，較早時已確認拜登是大選的明顯勝利者，可正式展開過渡工作。一直聲稱大選有舞弊，但沒有實質證據的特朗普，至今仍拒絕認輸，但強調聯邦總務署必須做要做的事情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561730-20201125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561730-20201125.htm&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=a8b68da3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561730-20201125.htm&h=67755c04\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561730-20201125.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4uGoag_4AHU/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F4uGoag_4AHU%2F0.jpg&h=d599b180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n信袁爸唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，繼續FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nydailynews.com/resizer/IJ9O-ysITZWQnXr8_CX1cJog64w=/415x276/top/cloudfront-us-east-1.images.arcpublishing.com/tronc/QBF2OUH75VGUHA3QMZF7NG6EKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nydailynews.com%2Fresizer%2FIJ9O-ysITZWQnXr8_CX1cJog64w%3D%2F415x276%2Ftop%2Fcloudfront-us-east-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Ftronc%2FQBF2OUH75VGUHA3QMZF7NG6EKE.jpg&h=0dcc3a08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd75384f0a28b747f0f90e807aab5246fc8af9f7","tid":2299584,"uid":37111